(8063, 1049, 'cac_cong_trinh_khoa_học_tieu_biểu', '<table class=\"ck-table-resized\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nguyen Vu Thanh, Dang Quoc Vuong, Truong Cong Trinh (2024). Performence Comparison Of A Six Phase Surface-Mounded Pmsm With Inner And Outer Rotor Types For High Torque Applications. Advance In Electrical and Electronic Engineering. DOI 10.15598/aeee.v22i2.5536</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nguyen Vu Thanh, Nguyen Trong Khoi (2024). Computation and Design of Detailed Sizing of Stator Slot Types Utilized in Axial Flux Permanent Magnet Machines. International Journal of Renewable Energy Research. DOI 10.20508/ijrer.v14i1.14327.g8861</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cong, Trinh &amp; Nguyen Vu, Thanh &amp; Pinto, Gabriel &amp; Quoc, Vuong. (2024). Optimization Design of Surface-mounted Permanent Magnet Synchronous Motors Using Genetic Algorithms. EAI Endorsed Transactions on Energy Web. 11. 10.4108/ew.4864.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Truong Cong, T., Nguyen Vu, T., Bui Minh, D., Vo Thanh, H., Dang Quoc, V. (2024). \'Analytical Modelling of a Six-Phase Surface Mounted Permanent Magnet Synchronous Motor\', International Journal of Engineering, 37(7), pp. 1274-1283. doi: 10.5829/ije.2024.37.07a.07</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Truong, T.C., Vu, T.N., Duc, H.B., Quoc, V.D. (2023). Using genetic algorithms for optimal electromagnetic parameters of SPM synchronous motors. Journal Européen des Systèmes Automatisés, Vol. 56, No. 6, pp. 899-906. https://doi.org/10.18280/jesa.560601</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Trinh Cong Truong, Thanh Nguyen Vu, Nam Le Hai, Thang Nguyen Duy, Duong Doan le Quy, Vuong Dang Quoc, Duc-Quang Nguyen and Bao Doan Thanh “Optimal Electromagnetic Parameters of SPMSM for Electric Vehicles Based on Genetic Algorithm Technique”, International Journal on Electrical Engineering and Informatics (IJEEI). Vol. 16 No. 1, pp.137-148, Scopus, Q3, SJR 2023: 0.28. Doi: 10.15676/ijeei.2024.16.1.9.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thanh Nguyen Vu, Truong Ngo Quang, Vuong Dang Quoc (2024). Investigate Influence of Slot-Pole Combination on the Voltage Total Harmonic Distortion of AFPM Generator with Concentrated Windings, 1/2024. DOI 10.1109/EEE-AM58328.2023.10395165</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>T. T. Cong, T. N. Vu, T. P. Anh and V. D. Quoc, \"Finite Element Approach for Computing Stray Fields in Magnetic Shielding Due to Non-Sinusoidal and DC Hybrid Excitations,\" 2023 12th International Conference on Control, Automation and Information Sciences (ICCAIS), Hanoi, Vietnam, 2023, pp. 272-277, doi: 10.1109/ICCAIS59597.2023.10382277.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nguyen Vu Thanh, Phung Anh Tuan, Ha Quang Viet, Ngo Duc Kien (2023). Analysis of magnetic features in IPMSM used for EV considering PM-flux barrier interaction and excitation current. Tạp chí Khoa học và Công nghệ-Đại học Đà Nẵng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Vu, T.N., Viet, T.N., Quoc, V.D. (2023). A Novel Approach for Determination of Main Dimensions and Armature Reactions of Axial Flux Permanent Magnet Generators. In: Nguyen, D.C., Vu, N.P., Long, B.T., Puta, H., Sattler, KU. (eds) Advances in Engineering Research and Application. ICERA 2022. Lecture Notes in Networks and Systems, vol 602. Springer, Cham. https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-031-22200-9_6</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Nguyen Vu, Thanh &amp; Quang, Truong &amp; Quoc, Vuong. (2023). Investigate Influence of Slot-Pole Combination on the Voltage Total Harmonic Distortion of AFPM Generator with Concentrated Windings. 1-7. 10.1109/EEE-AM58328.2023.10395165.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Hoang Anh, Duc Tung Trinh, Vu Thanh Nguyen, Hung Dung Pham, Duc Chinh Hoang. “A Cost-Effective Control System of the Biogas-Based Electrical Generator”. Springer, Singapore. DOI 10.1007/978-981-19-6450-3_7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>'),
