/li>\r\n 	<li>Phó trưởng khoa: <a href=\"https://seee.hust.edu.vn/vi/suborgans/person/Khoa-Tu-dong-hoa-5/PGS-Duong-Minh-Duc-62/\">PGS. TS. Dương Minh Đức</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Giới thiệu chung', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '326-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-05-14 03:17:09', '2025-05-14 03:17:09', '', 326, 'http://web-hust.test/?p=327', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
